<h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px;">Unlock Your Account</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>,</p>

<p>Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign-in attempts.</p>

<p>To unlock your account, please click the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <%= link_to 'Unlock My Account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token), class: 'button', style: 'display: inline-block; background-color: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;' %>
</div>

<p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following URL into your browser:</p>

<p style="margin: 15px 0; word-break: break-all; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">
  <%= unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %>
</p>

<p>After unlocking, you'll be able to sign in with your regular credentials.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>The Wheel Team</p>